{"tid":616962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[睇急症問題] 比野砸親隻腳趾應唔應該睇急症","createTime":"2018-04-04T15:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T05:47:44.000Z","uid":35324,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d3d2313675540bb414e1a00bbbcdae695613f812","tid":616962,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:20:53.000Z","msg":"而家隻腳趾瘀咗撻，屈唔到，用力就痛<br />\n但唔用力喺隻腳趾就仲行得走得<br />\n<br />\n驚砸到舊骨<br />\n如果因為一隻腳趾而去睇急症算落算濫用急症室服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係我應該過幾日等佢好返算<br />\n<br />\n聽日紅日急症室會唔會好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 為咗隻腳趾排幾個鐘......<br />\n我仲要去拜山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd802ef6b59727a6947b9c26a9cebd42a10dd2f","tid":616962,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:22:33.000Z","msg":"幾重既野 有無二三十KG"},{"pid":"3347fb72b0614e26a3b921046cb8d079fb660d01","tid":616962,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9fd802ef6b59727a6947b9c26a9cebd42a10dd2f","tid":616962,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:22:33.000Z","msg":"幾重既野 有無二三十KG"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:23:16.000Z","msg":"如果係咁我應該成隻腳都斷咗...<br />\n<br />\n幾kg啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90925b212da688d48cdc04df859a3fe39c548479","tid":616962,"uid":78253,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:24:53.000Z","msg":"而家去排天光差唔多有得睇"},{"pid":"24c29fec2adbf0ae80cf9aa8d5ea125bd795b5d0","tid":616962,"uid":78253,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:26:54.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n忍到就明天睇跌打果D<br />\n唔講濫唔濫用<br />\n去到D姑娘見你行得走得根本唔會理你<br />\n去到又大把PK感冒都睇急症<br />\n到時奶埋嘢仲衰<br />\n明天假期好多人得閒排"},{"pid":"0d4bedcc834f763da998b947d0f6d0e50ef29d52","tid":616962,"uid":137997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:27:28.000Z","msg":